{"tid":1344744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"身為元朗人的我 覺得好羞家","createTime":"2019-07-22T00:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:03:52.000Z","uid":62495,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b2659d6e35989356d798634124f8f0ceb162db59","tid":1344744,"uid":62495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:22:56.000Z","msg":"我住左元朗20幾年<br />\n一直都覺得元朗地方幾好<br />\n直到琴晚我估唔到我自己都要驚埋一份<br />\n我仲要特登去睇警局個門口係咪真係關左..<br />\n<br />\n一直以黎 元朗咁多唔同飯數<br />\n最多咪打下細交 吹下雞<br />\n一見D狗就會散 <br />\n<br />\n今次明目張膽到咁 仲要連狗都唔驚<br />\n大佬 人命黎架 真係打撚死人架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時邊飯打邊飯 點黑法<br />\n我都覺得算 已經存在咗咁多年<br />\n但係呢一刻為錢可以做到咁 為面可以咁過份？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我開始對自己係元朗人覺得羞家"},{"pid":"6aa7cefdcd65ac664dc70b0ea77c7ae0a36f59f2","tid":1344744,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:30:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">中共最叻以群眾鬥群眾，內耗消耗民意，<br />\n引起眾多火頭，燃起多條戰綫，力圖模糊最初目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"b170d001abbc65b94362e58a5d5db1f89663b2ef","tid":1344744,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:36:23.000Z","msg":"今次擺明d狗幫班白衫走架啦"},{"pid":"62e5ef617d5fe4e83f1794a0bc5a943847ac0bdb","tid":1344744,"uid":62495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b170d001abbc65b94362e58a5d5db1f89663b2ef","tid":1344744,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:36:23.000Z","msg":"今次擺明d狗幫班白衫走架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T00:42:35.000Z","msg":"我睇左成晚 到依家都訓唔著"},{"pid":"c1722c6b156aa0475c0fc606ce052177e7b5efae","tid":1344744,"uid":62495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:03:52.000Z","msg":"推推推"}]}